===Brazil vs Morocco===
The teams have met three times previously, including once in the World Cup, a [[1998 FIFA World Cup Group A#Brazil vs Morocco|3–0 first group stage victory]] for Brazil in [[1998 FIFA World Cup|1998]], and most recently in 2023, a 2–1 win for Morocco (their first) in a friendly.<ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil national football team: record v Morocco|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/brazil/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Morocco|website=11v11.com|access-date=December 5, 2025}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil vs. Morocco Head-to-Head in the World Cups|url=https://www.thesoccerworldcups.com/head_to_head/brazil_vs_morocco.php|website=thesoccerworldcups.com|access-date=December 5, 2025}}</ref>

